{"tid":1802451,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知1月1遊行人數有幾重要","createTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T00:00:01.000Z","uid":21220,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0590c7e445c287ca6c7dfa6c355711466599ec1c","tid":1802451,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"我知今次實又有人話咩人數唔係重點 冇得同200萬人嗰次比<br />\n<br />\n政府每次都冷處理遊行人數 無論係100萬人定係200萬人 因為佢地無言以對呀<br />\n<br />\n我想講 人數多真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n勇武同和理非手足見倒人數多係會好鼓舞倒士氣<br />\n<br />\n藍絲藍店見倒人數多會怕繼續被杯葛 怕黃色經濟圈繼續壯大<br />\n<br />\n外國見倒我們人數多證明我哋係好有決心繼續打呢場仗 會更加幫我地手<br />\n<br />\n今次遊行人數既多少 會展示我地繼續抗爭既決心<br />\n<br />\n同時亦會係一個預示 究竟我地仲可以打多幾耐<br />\n<br />\n為左香港 為左手足 麻煩大家出倒就出<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"3655a2ce696c428c88d8929df8a1e5673788844c","tid":1802451,"uid":3575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"83cb613e5f35cba97d310f2f9dad5e72339d797c","tid":1802451,"uid":84614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"1月1"},{"pid":"f9e273ef429ea4a9a1b3e4c3f4a07f4a3bc22323","tid":1802451,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"推，必出<br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港獨立  唯一出路</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783651a63acfd4519e121b870b84bb37a589047a","tid":1802451,"uid":84614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"維園見"},{"pid":"bb51db257410daf21ace902eff3aa87d7e5c2d64","tid":1802451,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c5bde683748ade4f101cb1cf217a0907deb4be","tid":1802451,"uid":156